overview: Jimmy is a 42-year-old man-child who hasn't progressed in life since losing the senior class president election 25 years ago to the now current Governor of Texas. Frustrated, Jimmy decides to go back to high school and run for class president again. However, when he tries to adapt to the pace of Gen Z and TikTok, he realizes that he has lots to learn beyond the proper use of gender pronouns.
title: Re-Election
